snippet.title: Arena Breakout - Official Season 2 Update Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Watch the latest trailer for Arena Breakout for a peek at what to expect with the Season 2 update for the mobile tactical FPS. Arena Breakout is available now on iOS and Android devices, and the Season 2 update will be available in October 2023.
